20:10.020 --> 20:13.140
I know the ship he was on was the Christine Wheeler.

20:13.540 --> 20:15.860
And who's going to know what that means, you know?

20:15.860 --> 20:20.840
Yeah, well, I should revise versions of that every 10 years, you know.

20:21.160 --> 20:23.480
But there was the good ship Trotsky.

20:23.600 --> 20:24.300
That'll stand.

20:24.600 --> 20:29.420
I mean, I also, the British edition, the Golden Thread, the use of Christine Heeler,

